{"tid":2106482,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[點解會係黃?] hktvmall由頭到尾既作風都係不折不扣既藍店","createTime":"2020-07-13T11:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T13:27:07.000Z","uid":7854,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bad8cfb52bc8766b588e11017f63c68b246ea970","tid":2106482,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"長話短說<br />\n<br />\n1) 成日講到自己最大型幾多生意<br />\n但連一個Cs電話都無<br />\n文字Cs? 等半個鍾都唔知連到未<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 無良銷售, 只要你一落單就唔俾你取消<br />\n唔講話幾多日無條件退款果d<br />\n<br />\n間野手殘落錯單,10秒內想取消已經話唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3)2月缺口罩果時 俾人捉到賣疑似假口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1835257/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1835257/page/1</a><br />\n之後一句話我只係平台唔關我事<br />\n咁人地上架上枝槍上去係咪又唔關你事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 4)扮無辜其實就無良奸商<br />\n<br />\n2月缺口罩 hktvmall有部份鋪頭公然賣極高炒價口罩<br />\n<br />\nhktvmall就出黎扮正義話唔允許人地咁做<br />\n但佢只係平台阻唔到<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆全香港得你同ztore兩個最大平台<br />\n<br />\n你出到聲唔俾人炒價唔係就封鋪下架  唔通人地會唔妥協咩?"},{"pid":"2506cfc67ac262b51242815f729a7a6f44665530","tid":2106482,"uid":7854,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"5)<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zxz6rRK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxz6rRK.png&h=e9a5080d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6) 3月高調話為香港人整口罩 香港良心啊~<br />\n<br />\n點知到最後就唔知公開賣左幾多個<br />\n<br />\n成日要人買滿幾舊水先施捨10個口罩想促銷做生意就真<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2615000/2615672/200410_HKTV_01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2615000%2F2615672%2F200410_HKTV_01_600.jpg&h=5972d39f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e4f2797359d249df11b986f14cb13c02823c43a","tid":2106482,"uid":7854,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKNvTxt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKNvTxt.png&h=f832209b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7)仲衰過藍店 當人做奴隸坐監啊?洗唔洗 廁所set埋cam俾你睇有無偷懶啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d8a6da71b369713de4e7add72910846c73612e","tid":2106482,"uid":239696,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:13:49.000Z","msg":"傻閪以為打大段野等於有Point<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24cb358c49259ad6a9c4bbd8e789aeb5103be14","tid":2106482,"uid":29741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}